    "isAvailable": true,
    "featureBullets": [
      "Triple Action Foundation - No7's medium to full coverage foundation with SPF 15 instantly gives skin a firmer, brighter-looking appearance and contains optical blurring technology to help reflect light away from fine lines and wrinkles. Formulated with Skin Expert\u2122 technology and available in 18 shades.",
      "Skin-Loving Ingredients - This tinted serum foundation contains vitamin A, C & E to help brighten the appearance of skin and leave you with a radiant glow. Hibiscus is another active ingredient, working to enhance the skin's ability to retain moisture. Lastly, this SPF foundation contains No7's collagen-based peptide technology, MATRIXYL 3000 PLUS\u2122 for a more youthful-looking complexion.",
      "Clinical Results - 114 respondents found that after 4 weeks of using this face makeup, 93% saw a visible reduction in the appearance of age spots, 85% saw a visible reduction in the appearance of fine lines and 91% saw that their skin looked firmer.*",
      "How to Use - Dot a little bit of the hydrating foundation where you need it most, usually your cheeks, nose and chin. Blend into skin with your No7 Flawless Finishing Blending Sponge or No7 Foundation Brush in a small circular motion, working downwards and outwards from the center of your face.",
      "Empowering Women Since 1935 - No7 has been creating beauty history by helping women look and feel their best for decades. With our rich health and beauty heritage, innovative skincare, and makeup backed by science, we've become the trusted brand through the generations. No7 has always offered every woman luxurious and glamorous beauty at a price they can afford."
    ],
