        {
          "reviewTitle": "Perfect color match and smooth feel",
          "reviewText": "I was wary about choosing a new foundation online mostly because of color matching - but I have to say this is the very FIRST time I have a perfect color match! You can't see the difference at the hairline or jawline at all. I'm 60 years old and don't generally wear foundation on the daily because I don't like the way it feels on my skin and it always settles into my pores and fine lines. Not with this one! It's smooth and light, no color transfer and doesn't feel itchy, greasy or dry. It looks as good after several hours as it does the first hour and honestly does not look like I'm wearing foundation at all. Smooths my completion and makes me feel pretty.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2026",
