        {
          "reviewTitle": "Great foundation",
          "reviewText": "After coming to Amazon to purchase my color Morphe, this was suggested to me. I decided to try it and I love it. Perfect color and very buildable. Lasts all day on my face, I do have dry skin.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on February 18, 2026",
