          "helpfulVotes": "5 people found this helpful"
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Reduce those fine lines!",
          "reviewText": "Love this product! Purchased multiple times. I have maturing skin with many imperfections. This product covers those imperfections with a natural look and feel. Stays on through a 12 hour shift. I pair it with the No 7 airbrush away primer for longer lasting coverage. I have tried many expensive foundations, including IL MAKIAGE. Most are too thick which accentuates fine lines and wrinkles. As a woman in her 50s, I highly recommend this product for a more natural and lasting coverage that will not highlight those fine lines but make them less visible.",
